title: Pygmalion in Management
Ask HN How do I learn marketing?
text:
I'm a strong engineer, and that's my core skill. But I want to focus 75% of my time on marketing.

Is there a way to learn marketing, in the same way that one learns software engineering?

It's so easy to learn software engineering, and the results are instant. How can I apply the same learning concepts to marketing?

Tell HN: OpenAI removed all my ChatGPT history without telling me
text:
Everything is gone. In the left pane, I see no history. I had maybe 30 different chat histories which are now disappeared completely.

Crazy thing is, I still have a link to one of my chats and that works:

https://imgur.com/a/PCnLG6J

So I'm sure they still keep the chat histories on their servers even if it doesn't show in the history panel.
